data.text:
As the name says Is the air force of the Netherlands during the WW2, despite the capitulation of the country, the Dutch air force stay active for the whole conflicts being part of almost all the big operation in both Pacific and Europe

I suggest the squad itself to come as event for allies with the Fokker D.XXI as BR2 fighter

The Fokker D.XXI stats are

Flight performance

Max speed 425 km/h

Max altitude10 100 m

EngineBristol Mercury VIII

TypeRadial

Cooling systemAir

Take-off weight2t

Turn time 17.4

Climb 11.6

Offensive armament
